  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, randomized, control, open label study in which up to 50 subjects with
      metatarsus adductus (MTA) will be enrolled. Subjects will be treated with the standard
      casting or using the UNFO-s device for total time of 20 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
