  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with an acute MTA that did not receive any treatment for this condition

          -  Consenting parents

          -  Ages 1-4 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Participation in another clinical trial.

          -  Neuromuscular disorders

          -  Any condition which in the opinion of the investigator renders the subject ineligible
             for study participation.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
